                "actions": {
                    "value": ""
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A living humanoid slain by Valgomorus's claw Strike rises as a spawned wight after [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}. This spawned wight is under the command of the wight that killed it (in this case, Valgomorus). It doesn't have drain life or wight spawn and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} for as long as it is a spawned wight.</p>\n<p>If the creator of the spawned wight dies, the spawned wight becomes a full-fledged, autonomous wight; it regains its free will, gains drain life and wight spawn, and is no longer clumsy.</p>"
